name: bunny-pack
description: Decode MessagePack encoded messages in RabbitMQ's web console.

scripts.version: node -e "const fs=require('fs');const manifest=JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync('./manifest.json'));manifest.version=process.env.npm_package_version;fs.writeFileSync('./manifest.json',JSON.stringify(manifest,null,2));" && git add manifest.json package.json && git commit -m "v$npm_package_version"
